metadata.name: I SEE YOU
metadata.description:
Imagine a translucent bubble where you can see 
through all the layers, enveloped in the warmth of 
unconditional love that is there just below the surface, 
showing the beauty, depth, and complexity of the endless expanse of existence. 

A reminder to embrace the value of authenticity, 
to connect deeply, and to cherish the sanctuaries of love we create in a world that is always shifting.

2037 x 2666
